{"tid":1574784,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"百威亞太重啟上市，擬引入新加坡主權基金為基礎投資者。","createTime":"2019-09-16T14:46:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-17T12:00:27.000Z","uid":46504,"like":2,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"11d1d9d4344e05eece3f36ef6360fab09e29d0ec","tid":1574784,"uid":46504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T14:46:59.000Z","msg":"外電引述消息人士指，上周四（12日）宣布重啟上市申請的百威亞太，正引入新加坡主權基金GIC為基石投資者，投資約10億美元（約78億港元），最終金額仍有調整可能。事實上，其保薦人摩根士丹利曾於7月首次招股的新聞發布會上表示，「我們無需任何基石投資者」。<br />\n<br />\n有接近消息人士指，百威將於星期三（18日）開始招股，30日掛牌，摩根大通和摩根士丹利為上市保薦人，市傳百威將削減逾半集資額至50億美元（約390億港元）。<br />\n<br />\n咁多位ching 有點諗法<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />法"},{"pid":"49d336d25a95baec841ab07ce2e2834185c0fcbd","tid":1574784,"uid":263058,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T14:47:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"14562719b8069ec728f49cea060457fd858b4eab","tid":1574784,"uid":123713,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T14:47:18.000Z","msg":"915國旗行動好成功!<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1573307\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1573307</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4jR5wr1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4jR5wr1.jpg&h=d9b2c693&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6491710f5824a8e48bcf6cc43a0d04bbae6ed721","tid":1574784,"uid":33930,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T14:48:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pvsTHEi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpvsTHEi.jpg&h=e8bfe3ea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">宣佈 和你suck 4.0 9月22 星期日見<br />\n<br />\nsuck 4.0 將會基於 hkmap.live 行動  <br />\n麻煩力推呢個livemap <br />\n對各位日後行動都非常大幫助<br />\n<br />\n請各位必須係 9月22日當日12點30分留意channel / 連登 / IG 最新消息<br />\n